and lays the foundation for future work on aggregate models that can\nbalance computational cost with prediction accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2016 03:21:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2016 02:40:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-16"}
