plies that halo formation history has a small but statistically significant\nimpact on quenching of star formation at high masses, while the quenching\nprocess in low-mass central galaxies is uncorrelated with halo formation\nhistory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2016 13:28:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
